{"tid":2166581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"卡達菲殺平民武器 國際倡禁用","createTime":"2020-08-20T13:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T13:42:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"921817bf7092bb15156d1b4ad1a3718970cb5408","tid":2166581,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/SMN5HGIRJVEGROMHDZCWAXIZ6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FSMN5HGIRJVEGROMHDZCWAXIZ6E%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5XwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=54cbfe72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FSMN5HGIRJVEGROMHDZCWAXIZ6E%2F&h=8c17e677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/SMN5HGIRJVEGROMHDZCWAXIZ6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n卡達菲殺平民武器 國際倡禁用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pZh9EGeD4DZwGkCL70c3ZDjiBTc=/1310x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XR3RKLNZ2FFETB7IRZDACJDTOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpZh9EGeD4DZwGkCL70c3ZDjiBTc%3D%2F1310x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXR3RKLNZ2FFETB7IRZDACJDTOY.jpg&h=4e24e35b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■央視節目中展現「天雷500」的大殺傷力。<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】大陸傳媒過去曾形容集束彈「極度殘酷」，將大量小型炸彈集合成一般空用炸彈的形態，利用大量小型炸彈增加轟炸面積和殺傷範圍，主要以人體、沒有裝甲的車輛或器材為主要目標。利比亞已故狂人卡達菲生前曾用集束彈殘殺平民，美國也曾在阿富汗和伊拉克戰爭使用集束彈攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中美俄拒簽公約<br />\n<br />\n本報2016年報道珠海航展時，當時在中國北方工業公司展廳，也曾展出多款集束炸彈。國際曾提出禁制集束彈公約，挪威等國2008年曾發起《集束彈藥公約》，主張國家不得使用、開發和轉讓集束彈，並獲112個國家簽署，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f592fc6b261962edba74e2ab090c804957f457ae","tid":2166581,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"幾時連槍都禁埋"}]}